377
00:22:03,831 --> 00:22:06,466
<i>I'm sorry, don.
The decision's been made.</i>

378
00:22:06,534 --> 00:22:08,635
<i>I just thought
you should hear it from me.</i>

379
00:22:08,703 --> 00:22:10,637
