another shot at this soon.

380
00:22:10,705 --> 00:22:12,472
<i>As long as you're around.</i>

381
00:22:12,540 --> 00:22:14,508
We'll be here.
Don't worry.

382
00:22:14,575 --> 00:22:16,243
<i>Good luck, don.</i>

383
00:22:16,310 --> 00:22:18,345
<i>I hope we can work
together again sometime.</i>

384
00:22:18,412 --> 00:22:20,313
<i>- Okay.
- Goodbye.</i>

385
00:22:20,381 --> 00:22:21,414
Goodbye.

386
00:22:30,091 --> 00:22:32,692
<i>What was that?</i>

