399
00:23:10,398 --> 00:23:12,465
I don't know what the hell you
said to them this morning.

400
00:23:17,939 --> 00:23:21,408
So, Joan, that puts us at what?
20 million and change?

401
00:23:21,475 --> 00:23:23,510
Are you doubting my efforts?

402
00:23:23,578 --> 00:23:25,412
All you had to do was tell
them everything was fine.

403
00:23:25,479 --> 00:23:27,113
You think that call's
easy to make?

404
00:23:27,181 --> 00:23:28,982
I think you're distracted.

405
00:23:29,050 --> 00:23:30,617
Because of that, I think you
scared the shit out of 'em.

406
00:23:30,685 --> 00:23:32,652
Who the hell do you think
you're talking to?

407
00:23:54,742 --> 00:23:56,676
Don't blow a gasket.

408
00:23:56,744 --> 00:23:59,479
