the man of the hour.

412
00:24:08,522 --> 00:24:10,824
Ted. How considerate
of you to stop by.

413
00:24:10,891 --> 00:24:12,626
I wish the baby
was here already,

414
00:24:12,693 --> 00:24:14,194
But I'm sure everyone
feels that way.

415
00:24:14,262 --> 00:24:16,263
Good news is always
worth waiting for.

416
00:24:16,330 --> 00:24:19,199
Don't let
your vanity get the best of you.

417
00:24:19,267 --> 00:24:21,434
There is nothing wrong
with being called grandma.

418
00:24:26,407 --> 00:24:29,009
It's a rattle.
You can get it engraved.

419
00:24:29,076 --> 00:24:31,111
Ogilvy sent me one
when my son was born.

420
00:24:31,178 --> 00:24:33,847
Thank you.
What do you want, Ted?

421
00:24:33,914 --> 00:24:36,049
No, this is about
what you want.

