little Italian sports car.

441
00:25:21,162 --> 00:25:23,763
I don't know if you've heard of it, but I
think you'll really enjoy driving one.

442
00:25:23,831 --> 00:25:26,366
- I don't drive.
- I'll teach you.

443
00:25:26,434 --> 00:25:30,003
Tom, Jeannie,
my offer still stands.

444
00:25:30,071 --> 00:25:31,871
<i>If you want a hotel room, I can
get you one across the street.</i>

445
00:25:47,555 --> 00:25:50,056
Roger.
I let you come over

446
00:25:50,124 --> 00:25:52,525
