457
00:26:22,223 --> 00:26:24,290
Because I'm a port in a storm?

458
00:26:24,358 --> 00:26:27,794
No. Because I feel like
shit and you care about me.

459
00:26:27,862 --> 00:26:30,263
I'm not a solution
to your problems.

460
00:26:30,331 --> 00:26:32,699
I'm another problem.

461
00:26:32,767 --> 00:26:34,701
Are you serious?

462
00:26:34,769 --> 00:26:37,170
I can't do this anymore.

463
00:26:37,238 --> 00:26:39,873
You'll change your mind.
You'll see.

464
00:26:39,940 --> 00:26:41,274
I'm sorry.

